1
00:00:11,373 --> 00:00:15,776
<i>Hey boys, listen up!</i>

2
00:00:15,844 --> 00:00:20,372
<i>Humans aren't such a big deal</i>

3
00:00:21,083 --> 00:00:25,213
<i>Who needs tomorrow anyway,</i>

4
00:00:25,287 --> 00:00:28,484
<i>so don't hide your fists</i>

5
00:00:30,425 --> 00:00:32,689
<i>You're not old enough</i>

6
00:00:32,761 --> 00:00:39,064
<i>to sell your dreams away to uncertainty</i>

7
00:00:40,002 --> 00:00:44,439
<i>Hey boys, you're the only ones</i>

8
00:00:44,506 --> 00:00:48,033
<i>who can pull the trigger in your heart</i>

9
00:00:49,478 --> 00:00:51,412
<i>All the kids said</i>

10
00:00:51,480 --> 00:00:54,415
<i>We're living in this senseless, ridiculous,</i>

11
00:00:54,483 --> 00:00:58,783
<i>awesome world right at this moment,</i>

12
00:00:58,987 --> 00:01:01,251
<i>All the kids said</i>

13
00:01:01,323 --> 00:01:07,125
<i>Don't forget every truth or lie</i>

14
00:01:08,530 --> 00:01:10,866
<i>All the kids said</i>

15
00:01:10,866 --> 00:01:13,198
<i>We're way too young to die</i>

16
00:01:13,268 --> 00:01:18,069
<i>In this empty town lined with empty faces</i>

17
00:01:18,140 --> 00:01:20,335
<i>All the kids took off</i>

18
00:01:20,409 --> 00:01:22,877
<i>into this windless night</i>

19
00:01:22,944 --> 00:01:26,311
<i>Because they want to change something</i>

20
00:01:30,930 --> 00:01:34,525
<i>For a Friend!</i>

21
00:01:35,835 --> 00:01:37,496
What did you say?!

22
00:01:37,770 --> 00:01:40,637
You mean to say that only rookies
went after Sasuke?!

23
00:01:41,374 --> 00:01:43,274
It really couldn't be helped...

24
00:01:43,343 --> 00:01:46,141
the situation in
the Village being how it is...

25
00:01:51,651 --> 00:01:53,050
And anyway...

26
00:01:53,286 --> 00:01:55,948
I've taken the minimally
required measures.

27
00:02:01,194 --> 00:02:02,354
Hey, hey!

28
00:02:02,428 --> 00:02:05,192
Your mission has already
been assigned!

29
00:02:05,265 --> 00:02:08,325
Uh, I'm gonna go do an errand
and will be back shortly...

30
00:02:08,635 --> 00:02:10,694
Don't worry.

31
00:02:16,042 --> 00:02:17,009
Geez...

32
00:02:22,649 --> 00:02:24,048
Kakashi Sensei!

33
00:02:25,585 --> 00:02:27,052
Kakashi Sensei!

34
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:32,148
It's already been two days
since Sasuke left the village...

35
00:02:32,825 --> 00:02:35,453
And Naruto and the others who went in
pursuit haven't come back either.

36
00:02:35,962 --> 00:02:37,691
And neither has Lee...

37
00:02:38,197 --> 00:02:41,291
I know. I've more or less
heard the whole story.

38
00:02:42,368 --> 00:02:46,099
I... believe in Naruto!

39
00:02:47,106 --> 00:02:50,769
I believe him, but if something were
to happen to Naruto and Sasuke...

40
00:02:54,580 --> 00:02:57,447
Sakura, you don't need to
worry about anything.

41
00:02:58,117 --> 00:02:59,914
Leave this to me.

42
00:03:17,003 --> 00:03:18,368
Summoning Jutsu!

43
00:03:30,450 --> 00:03:32,441
First of all, I want you guys to
fan out in all directions

44
00:03:32,518 --> 00:03:34,884
in pursuit of Naruto
and Sasuke's scent.

45
00:03:35,488 --> 00:03:37,752
Naruto and Sasuke you said?

46
00:03:38,624 --> 00:03:40,524
Did something happen
to the two of them?

47
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:44,589
I'll explain later...
Right now, time is of essence.

48
00:03:45,498 --> 00:03:46,487
Okay.

49
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:49,200
As soon as you confirm that
you've detected the scent,

50
00:03:49,268 --> 00:03:51,293
call me and I'll be there immediately.

51
00:03:52,305 --> 00:03:53,738
All right! Scatter!

52
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:08,210
<i>Well, I guess since she saw them</i>
<i>fight before her very eyes...</i>

53
00:04:08,287 --> 00:04:10,881
<i>it's useless to tell her</i>
<i>not to worry.</i>

54
00:04:17,330 --> 00:04:18,957
<i>Stop!</i>

55
00:04:23,102 --> 00:04:24,034
Damn...

56
00:04:24,470 --> 00:04:25,960
I can't stop...

57
00:04:45,725 --> 00:04:49,491
<i>Sasuke... Stop with revenge.</i>

58
00:04:49,595 --> 00:04:50,562
<i>What?!</i>

59
00:04:51,697 --> 00:04:54,063
<i>Even if you were successful</i>
<i>in carrying out your revenge,</i>

60
00:04:54,133 --> 00:04:55,862
<i>all that will come out of it</i>
<i>is a sense of emptiness.</i>

61
00:04:56,002 --> 00:04:57,196
<i>Shut up!</i>

62
00:04:57,270 --> 00:04:58,999
<i>What do you know?!</i>

63
00:04:59,305 --> 00:05:02,297
<i>Don't say that so knowingly!</i>

64
00:05:02,375 --> 00:05:04,605
<i>Well...calm down.</i>

65
00:05:05,211 --> 00:05:08,237
<i>Neither you nor I could</i>
<i>call ourselves lucky.</i>

66
00:05:09,082 --> 00:05:10,481
<i>Of that much I'm certain.</i>

67
00:05:11,784 --> 00:05:14,082
<i>But it could be worse.</i>

68
00:05:15,321 --> 00:05:19,951
<i>Both you and I have found</i>
<i>precious comrades, right?</i>

69
00:05:23,463 --> 00:05:26,193
<i>We understand that all the more</i>
<i>because we've lost them once.</i>

70
00:05:26,432 --> 00:05:27,899
<i>I taught you Chidori</i>

71
00:05:27,967 --> 00:05:31,334
<i>because you now have</i>
<i>precious people.</i>

72
00:05:32,872 --> 00:05:37,172
<i>That power isn't something to be used</i>
<i>against your comrades or for revenge.</i>

73
00:05:37,610 --> 00:05:41,307
<i>You know what that power</i>
<i>should be used for.</i>

74
00:05:42,115 --> 00:05:43,742
<i>I'm gonna win no matter what!</i>

75
00:05:43,816 --> 00:05:45,716
<i>Don't get so carried away!</i>

76
00:05:47,587 --> 00:05:49,054
<i>I was too naïve...</i>

77
00:05:50,556 --> 00:05:53,047
<i>Watching them, they might actually</i>
<i>be intent on killing each other...</i>

78
00:06:04,604 --> 00:06:05,832
<i>Kakashi Sensei...</i>

79
00:06:11,911 --> 00:06:13,435
<i>Please let me get there</i>
<i>in time!</i>

80
00:06:28,127 --> 00:06:29,685
I already said this earlier but...

81
00:06:31,964 --> 00:06:34,933
In truth, you were waiting
for this too, weren't you?

82
00:06:36,569 --> 00:06:38,799
Neither Kakashi nor Sakura
are present right now.

83
00:06:40,239 --> 00:06:43,367
So there's nobody here to stop us
like that time before.

84
00:06:44,076 --> 00:06:45,236
You...!

85
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:50,007
This time around we're gonna
settle this for real!

86
00:06:52,185 --> 00:06:53,652
I will take you down!

87
00:07:03,529 --> 00:07:04,587
Chidori!

88
00:07:11,137 --> 00:07:12,764
<i>You idiot...</i>

89
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:18,336
Same here!
I'm gonna clobber you...

90
00:07:18,411 --> 00:07:21,073
and take you back home even
if I have to drag you!

91
00:07:21,847 --> 00:07:23,712
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

92
00:07:37,230 --> 00:07:38,629
Rasengan!

93
00:08:20,239 --> 00:08:21,797
<i>It wasn't meaningless...</i>

94
00:08:22,675 --> 00:08:27,305
<i>To me, you became</i>
<i>my closest friend.</i>

95
00:08:28,547 --> 00:08:33,484
<i>Sasuke actually came out</i>
<i>and said that...to me...</i>

96
00:08:33,552 --> 00:08:37,750
<i>And that's exactly the reason why</i>
<i>I wanted to verify it using this Rasengan.</i>

97
00:08:58,544 --> 00:08:59,875
<i>Damn...</i>

98
00:09:01,681 --> 00:09:03,376
<i>Damn you!</i>

99
00:09:24,503 --> 00:09:26,095
<i>Damn...</i>

100
00:09:26,172 --> 00:09:28,606
<i>He was able to counter</i>

101
00:09:28,674 --> 00:09:30,665
<i>my full power of Chidori</i>
<i>to that extent...</i>

102
00:09:32,678 --> 00:09:33,940
<i>That jutsu...</i>

103
00:09:46,225 --> 00:09:47,385
<i>Damn...</i>

104
00:09:50,930 --> 00:09:54,093
<i>Naruto, to what extent...!</i>

105
00:09:56,869 --> 00:09:59,030
<i>That loser...</i>

106
00:10:06,579 --> 00:10:07,841
<i>Naruto...!</i>

107
00:10:16,722 --> 00:10:21,250
<i>Well, your limit is two blows...</i>
<i>that's about it.</i>

108
00:10:24,196 --> 00:10:26,528
<i>And if I try to use more than that...</i>

109
00:10:27,066 --> 00:10:28,226
<i>what will happen?</i>

110
00:10:30,002 --> 00:10:32,334
<i>The third blow won't initiate.</i>

111
00:10:33,038 --> 00:10:34,266
<i>Remember that well.</i>

112
00:10:35,608 --> 00:10:38,168
<i>If you try to initiate</i>
<i>the Jutsu forcibly...</i>

113
00:10:38,244 --> 00:10:40,678
<i>not only will the Art not</i>
<i>initiate properly,</i>

114
00:10:40,746 --> 00:10:42,737
<i>but your Chakra will become zero...</i>

115
00:10:42,815 --> 00:10:45,147
<i>In the worst case scenario</i>
<i>it will cost you your life!</i>

116
00:10:46,852 --> 00:10:50,515
<i>Damn... I can't waste a blow...</i>

117
00:10:51,157 --> 00:10:53,990
<i>It wouldn't serve any purpose</i>
<i>if we cancel each other like earlier.</i>

118
00:11:01,233 --> 00:11:05,431
<i>There's...no longer</i>
<i>any mistake about this.</i>

119
00:11:11,944 --> 00:11:15,380
<i>You...really intended...</i>

120
00:11:25,758 --> 00:11:27,692
<i>You really intended to...</i>

121
00:11:37,002 --> 00:11:38,367
<i>Sasuke...!</i>

122
00:11:43,609 --> 00:11:47,067
<i>I will use numerous speedy techniques</i>
<i>and Jutsu to create an opening.</i>

123
00:11:49,715 --> 00:11:52,411
<i>And then...I will make</i>
<i>a hit with Chidori.</i>

124
00:11:56,155 --> 00:11:57,645
<i>Sasuke...</i>

125
00:12:07,399 --> 00:12:09,697
Did you know, Naruto...

126
00:12:11,036 --> 00:12:15,530
Top class Ninja should be
able to read each other's hearts

127
00:12:15,608 --> 00:12:18,236
simply by an exchange of fists.

128
00:12:21,914 --> 00:12:23,848
Even without saying anything...

129
00:12:30,489 --> 00:12:33,390
You're naïve, Naruto.

130
00:12:36,996 --> 00:12:38,122
How about it?

131
00:12:39,532 --> 00:12:42,865
Were you really able
to read inside...

132
00:12:42,935 --> 00:12:44,994
this heart of mine?

133
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:50,436
<i>Fire Style.</i>
<i>Phoenix Flower Jutsu!</i>

134
00:13:11,096 --> 00:13:15,226
<i>Sasuke... I knew that you</i>
<i>were always alone.</i>

135
00:13:17,436 --> 00:13:20,234
<i>At first, I was relieved</i>
<i>when I found out</i>

136
00:13:20,306 --> 00:13:23,833
<i>that there was</i>
<i>a guy similar to myself.</i>

137
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:30,981
<i>And it also made me happy...</i>

138
00:13:31,917 --> 00:13:34,408
<i>To tell the truth, I really wanted</i>
<i>to approach you right away.</i>

139
00:13:37,923 --> 00:13:42,758
<i>But...I wasn't able to approach you...</i>

140
00:13:45,397 --> 00:13:47,058
- Awesome...
- You're incredible...

141
00:13:47,333 --> 00:13:49,267
<i>You were always able</i>
<i>to do everything.</i>

142
00:13:50,469 --> 00:13:53,905
<i>And moreover, you were always</i>
<i>being praised by everyone.</i>

143
00:14:06,885 --> 00:14:09,911
<i>Because you and I</i>
<i>were so different...</i>

144
00:14:10,856 --> 00:14:14,656
<i>Because I didn't want to admit it,</i>
<i>I decided to call you my rival.</i>

145
00:14:18,397 --> 00:14:19,989
<i>I didn't want to lose to you...</i>

146
00:14:21,066 --> 00:14:22,863
<i>and I felt that even more strongly...</i>

147
00:14:22,935 --> 00:14:25,301
<i>because I was called a loser.</i>

148
00:14:27,740 --> 00:14:30,265
<i>Even when we were</i>
<i>in the Squad Seven,</i>

149
00:14:30,342 --> 00:14:32,674
<i>I continued to feel</i>
<i>the same way the whole time.</i>

150
00:14:33,078 --> 00:14:35,137
<i>I'm stubborn...</i>

151
00:14:36,382 --> 00:14:39,283
<i>And wasn't able to express</i>
<i>what I really felt...</i>

152
00:14:42,087 --> 00:14:46,285
<i>What I really wanted was</i>
<i>to become like you.</i>

153
00:14:47,226 --> 00:14:53,722
<i>You were what I aspired to...so...</i>

154
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:57,862
<i>You are one of the ones</i>
<i>I want to fight.</i>

155
00:14:58,904 --> 00:15:03,034
<i>I was really happy when</i>
<i>you said that!</i>

156
00:15:04,476 --> 00:15:09,675
<i>Those were your first words...</i>
<i>acknowledging me...</i>

157
00:15:16,155 --> 00:15:18,589
<i>You and I both knew,</i>

158
00:15:18,657 --> 00:15:21,626
<i>without us even having to</i>
<i>have an exchange of fists!</i>

159
00:15:22,895 --> 00:15:24,419
<i>From that time on...</i>

160
00:15:25,297 --> 00:15:26,992
<i>Even without saying anything...</i>

161
00:15:29,702 --> 00:15:31,260
<i>The fact that...</i>

162
00:15:31,804 --> 00:15:33,897
<i>we are friends!</i>

163
00:15:37,943 --> 00:15:39,501
<i>It's not without meaning...</i>

164
00:15:40,646 --> 00:15:42,409
<i>To me you're...</i>

165
00:15:44,783 --> 00:15:47,411
<i>my closest friend.</i>

166
00:15:48,387 --> 00:15:53,450
<i>However...you're trying to</i>
<i>take me down for real.</i>

167
00:15:54,426 --> 00:15:55,791
<i>Right now, I don't really know</i>

168
00:15:55,861 --> 00:16:00,594
<i>whether you really meant</i>
<i>what you said earlier or not.</i>

169
00:16:04,369 --> 00:16:07,497
<i>Thinking that we were friends...</i>

170
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,535
<i>That might have been...</i>

171
00:16:11,110 --> 00:16:13,578
<i>That might have been just me...</i>

172
00:16:16,181 --> 00:16:17,978
It's too late now!

173
00:16:18,550 --> 00:16:19,847
Naruto!

174
00:16:28,093 --> 00:16:31,324
<i>If that's the case...I'm...</i>

175
00:16:35,634 --> 00:16:39,263
<i>really lame, am I not...</i>

176
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:43,105
<i>Sasuke!</i>

177
00:16:59,525 --> 00:17:00,583
<i>But...</i>

178
00:17:00,659 --> 00:17:02,251
<i>It can't be helped, can it?</i>

179
00:17:38,597 --> 00:17:40,895
<i>I don't know why but...</i>

180
00:17:44,269 --> 00:17:46,396
<i>I don't know why...</i>

181
00:17:47,139 --> 00:17:48,333
<i>But I...</i>

182
00:17:52,711 --> 00:17:54,042
<i>I...</i>

183
00:17:59,284 --> 00:18:00,979
<i>don't want you...</i>

184
00:18:04,323 --> 00:18:08,657
<i>you to be taken away</i>
<i>by someone like Orochimaru!</i>

185
00:18:25,711 --> 00:18:28,737
You managed to divert it
with your left hand,

186
00:18:29,181 --> 00:18:31,240
but it was meaningless.

187
00:18:34,620 --> 00:18:37,088
You won't be able to use
any hand sign

188
00:18:37,155 --> 00:18:39,419
or that Jutsu earlier anymore.

189
00:18:46,398 --> 00:18:47,660
<i>This is the end!</i>

190
00:19:07,886 --> 00:19:09,285
<i>Wh-What's...</i>

191
00:19:09,788 --> 00:19:11,517
<i>that red Chakra...?</i>

192
00:19:16,061 --> 00:19:18,359
<i>Where does he get that</i>
<i>kind of power from?!</i>

193
00:20:00,072 --> 00:20:03,508
<i>W-What the heck...is this?!</i>

194
00:20:06,678 --> 00:20:10,375
<i>His shoulder injury is healing...</i>

195
00:20:12,985 --> 00:20:14,282
<i>That's unbelievable!</i>

196
00:20:45,183 --> 00:20:52,089
Sasuke! I'm not gonna let
Orochimaru take you away!

197
00:20:54,993 --> 00:20:56,585
I will stop you,

198
00:20:56,661 --> 00:21:01,963
even if I have to break every bone
in your arms and legs!

199
00:21:12,477 --> 00:21:17,141
<i>When I recalled the parts one by one,</i>

200
00:21:17,215 --> 00:21:23,518
<i>I felt as though</i>
<i>I had understood everything</i>

201
00:21:23,588 --> 00:21:34,089
<i>Faded words which I kept so close to me</i>

202
00:21:34,399 --> 00:21:43,865
<i>Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,</i>

203
00:21:45,610 --> 00:21:50,604
<i>and this distant yearning for you</i>

204
00:21:50,916 --> 00:21:59,915
<i>I live, simply repeating this cycle</i>

205
00:22:02,094 --> 00:22:11,628
<i>Held in my two hands</i>
<i>A droplet of time</i>

206
00:22:13,071 --> 00:22:22,070
<i>Softly clutching forgotten memories</i>
<i>Lost words</i>

207
00:22:30,956 --> 00:22:34,824
<i>I'll keep these thoughts...</i>

208
00:22:40,899 --> 00:22:42,992
Don't you talk stupid like that!

209
00:22:43,268 --> 00:22:46,965
I don't care what
you're thinking anymore!

210
00:22:47,272 --> 00:22:49,968
I won't let you go to Orochimaru's
place no matter what!

211
00:22:50,408 --> 00:22:55,004
I'm taking you back to the village
even if I have to drag you there!

212
00:22:55,780 --> 00:22:58,442
Sasuke! You're my...

213
00:22:59,017 --> 00:23:03,386
Next episode: "A Plea From a Friend"
